description:

NebulaDream, compared to Nebulav1.0, has added a greater variety of stunning and colorful artistic styles of nebula images to its training set. Additionally, it has become more stable, resulting in even more dazzling generated images.

The higher the weight, the more prominent the nebula elements will be in the generated images. You can choose the weight based on your preferences, and values between 0 and 1 will not cause any image distortions or issues.
